#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "The User Interface"
msgstr "Korisnički interfejs"

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:5
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The &kapp; Main Window"
msgid "The &kxstitch; Main Window"
msgstr "&kapp; Glavni prozor"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: ui.docbook:8
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Here's a screen shot of &kapp;"
msgid "Here's a screen shot of &kxstitch;"
msgstr "Ovo je slika ekrana za &kapp;"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:12
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The &kapp; main window consists of an editor window shown on the right in "
#| "the image above with three dock windows. The dock windows provide a "
#| "preview of the pattern, the palette of flosses and a history list. If an "
#| "image is imported, an additional dock window showing a preview of the "
#| "original image for reference will be shown. Each of these dock windows "
#| "can be moved around to various edges of the main window, detached from "
#| "the view or turned off and back on."
msgid ""
"The &kxstitch; main window consists of an editor window shown on the right "
"in the image above with three dock windows. The dock windows provide a "
"preview of the pattern, the palette of flosses and a history list. If an "
"image is imported, an additional dock window showing a preview of the "
"original image for reference will be shown. Each of these dock windows can "
"be moved around to various edges of the main window, detached from the view "
"or turned off and back on."
msgstr ""
"&Kapp; Glavni prozor se sastoji od prozora editora koji je prikazan na "
"desnoj strani na slici gore sa tri prozora. Taj prozor omogućava pregled "
"uzoraka, palete konaca i spisak historije. Ako je slika iz uvoza, bit će "
"prikazan dodatni prozor koji prikazuje pregled originalne slike. Svaki od "
"ovih prozora može biti premješten na raznim rubovima glavnog prozora, "
"odvojen od prikaza ili isključen."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sections are divided by splitters, which can be moved to change the "
"amount of space allocated to any of the sections."
msgstr ""
"Odijeli su odvojeni \"drvima\", koja mogu biti premještena, tako da se "
"promijeni količina prostora dodijeljena bilo kojem odjelu."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The layout of other elements, menu bar, toolbars and the status bar, is "
"similar to other &kde; applications you run."
msgstr ""
"Okvir ostalih elemenata, menija, alatne trake i statusa, slicna je drugim na "
"&kde; aplikacije koju pokrećete."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The status bar at the bottom of the window shows various status messages."
msgstr "Statusna traka na dnu prozora prikazuje različite poruke."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor Window"
msgstr ""
"Sliku možete umetnuti kao pozadinu na prozoru editora. Ovo je korisno ako "
"uvoz slike nije poželjan ili daje loše rezultate."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main editing window shows a grid pattern and scales top and left. The "
"scales can be formatted in stitches, centimeters or inches. The editor is a "
"scrolling, zoomable view of your pattern and allows you to use the various "
"editing tools to modify your design."
msgstr ""
"Glavni  prozor za uređivanjeprikazuje mrežu obrazaca i reda  od vrha pa "
"nalijevo. Skale se mogu formatirati u šavovima, centimetrima ili inčima. "
"Urednik se može zumirati i omogućava vam da koristite različite alate za "
"uređivanje da bi modificirali svoj dizajn."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Generally the &LMB; is used to activate any of the tools on the pattern. "
"Details of each of the tools and their use is shown in <link linkend="
"\"commands\">the command reference section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Generalno &LMB; korišten je za aktivaciju nekog od alata obrasca. Detalji o "
"svakom alatu i o njihovoj upotrebu možete vidjeti na : <link linkend="
"\"commands\"> dio o komandama </link>."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The grid shows heavier lines dividing the cells into groups. The number of "
"cells per group is configurable, the default is 10, as are the colors for "
"the lines. This is useful if you are creating patterns on a dark colored "
"canvas that requires lighter colored lines for contrast."
msgstr ""
"Rešetka pokazuje deblje linije dijeljenjem ćelije u grupe. Broj ćelija po "
"grupi je moguće podesiti, default je 10, kao što su i boje za linije. Ovo je "
"korisno ako se stvaraju obrasci na tamnom platnu koje zahtijeva lakše boje "
"linije za kontrast."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A menu option allows you to add background images to the editor window, to "
"use as a template for adding stitches. For more details see the section on "
"<link linkend=\"creatingpatterns\">Creating Patterns</link>."
msgstr ""
"Meni opcija vam omogućava da dodate pozadinske slike na prozor editora, koje "
"se koristite kao predložak za dodavanje šavova. Za više detalja pogledajte "
"poglavlje <link linkend=\"creatingpatterns\"> Kreiranje obrazaca </link> ."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:54 ui.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context Menu"
msgstr "Dodatne ikone na sadržajnom meniju su:"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using your &RMB; on the editor will activate a context menu allowing you to "
"change the format of the scales and the visual appearance of the stitches. "
"It also allows you to toggle on or off the background images, the stitches, "
"backstitches, the grid and the scales."
msgstr ""
"Upotrebom &RMB; na uredniku će aktivirati kontekst meni koji vam omogućava "
"da promijenite format skale i vizuelni izgled šavova. Također vam omogućava "
"da uključite ili isključite pozadinske slike, šavove, duple šavove, mrežu i "
"skalu."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview Window"
msgstr "Prikaži ili skrij prozor za pregled"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Preview</guilabel> window shows a scrolling overview of the "
"current design at a smaller scale than the Editor window. The "
"<guilabel>Preview</guilabel> shows a black rectangle representing the "
"current view within the Editor window."
msgstr ""
"The <guilabel> Pregled </guilabel> prozor pokazuje padajući pregled "
"trenutnog dizajna u manjem obimu nego editor. <guilabel> Pregled </guilabel> "
"pokazuje crni pravokutnik koji predstavlja trenutni prikaz unutar editora."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By clicking the &LMB; within the preview window, the Editor window will be "
"centered on that point. Additionally by pressing down the &LMB; and dragging "
"a rectangle around an area, the Editor window will be zoomed to encompass "
"that area."
msgstr ""
"Klikom na &LMB; u prozoru za pregled, prozor Editora će biti centriran. "
"Pored toga pritiskom na &LMB; i povlačenjem pravokutnika oko područja, "
"prozor će Editora se može zumirati da obuhvati to područje."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Palette Window"
msgstr "Prikaži ili skrij prozor palete"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Palette</guilabel> window shows the floss colors currently in "
"this patterns palette as colored blocks, and optionally with the symbols "
"that are associated with each color. Moving the mouse pointer over a color "
"block will pop up a tool tip showing the color number and name for that "
"color. Clicking on a color selects that color for the next painting or "
"drawing function."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel> Paleta </guilabel> prozor prikazuje konac trenutne boje u ovom "
"obrascu paleta kao obojene blokove, i opcijski sa simbolima koji su povezani "
"sa svake boje. Premještanjem pokazivača miša preko bloka u boji će se "
"pojaviti alat koji prikazuje broj boje i ime za tu boju. Klikom na boju bira "
"tu boju za sljedeću sliku ili crtež."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using your &RMB; on the <guilabel>Palette</guilabel> view will activate a "
"context menu allowing you to perform several functions on the palette. See "
"<link linkend=\"commands\">the command reference</link> for more details on "
"their use."
msgstr ""
"Korištenjem &RMB; na <guilabel>Paleta</guilabel> će aktivirati sadržajni "
"meni dozvoljavajući da se izvršavaju neke funkcije sa palete. Vidi <link "
"linkend=\"commands\">komande</link> za još detalja o njihovoj upotrebi."
